<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>500 — Erreur serveur</title>
    <style>
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body { font-family: Nunito, sans-serif; background: linear-gradient(to top, #c39be3, #f2eafa); min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
        .container { text-align: center; padding: 2rem; }
        h1 { font-size: 5rem; font-weight: 800; color: #1a1a2e; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        h4 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: #4361ee; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        p { color: #555; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        a { display: inline-block; background: #4361ee; color: #fff; padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
        a:hover { background: #3251d4; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>500</h1>
        <h4>Erreur interne</h4>
        <p>Une erreur inattendue s'est produite. Veuillez réessayer ou contacter l'administrateur.</p>
        <a href="/">Retour à l'accueil</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
